  <description>
    <p>
        Mattermost is a secure collaboration platform that is open,
        flexible, and deeply integrated with the tools you love.
        An alternative to SaaS collaboration solutions,
        Mattermost is built explicitly for developer teams, tools, and workflows.
        It is written in Golang and React and runs as a production-ready Linux binary
        under an MIT license with either MySQL or Postgres.
    </p>
